We are accepting a few more people for the month of july, we accept all skill levels from never traded before to trading for years! **This program includes:**
- 1 on 1 sessions to assess and evaluate your current skill level and what you need to work on
- Filling in your knowledge gaps 
- Creating a sound trading strategy to make you consistently profitable
- Teaching you how to use technical indicators 
- Teaching you the ins and outs of screeners
- Constant learning even after the first month
- Access to all my live training classes for free as well as the recordings. 

**For those of you unfamiliar with my trading style and gains, heres my trade tracker** 
https://tinyurl.com/moneybagstradetracker

-Technical Indicator Types

- How to use these indicators

Class 1
- What you need to start day trading

- Importance of using a screener

Class 2 
-Typical start of the trading day 
- Importance of screeners

- Rules on momentum Day trading
